title: Bump collation `in_peers` to 300 for the experimental collator protocol
doc:
- audience: Node Dev
  description: |
    Bump `MAX_AUTHORITY_INCOMING_STREAMS` in peer_set to be in line with `CONNECTED_PEERS_PARA_LIMIT`
    in experimental collator protocol.
crates:
- name: cumulus-relay-chain-minimal-node
  bump: patch
- name: polkadot-collator-protocol
  bump: patch
- name: polkadot-node-network-protocol
  bump: patch
- name: polkadot-service
  bump: patch
